Develop text NLP and ML applications for various Zoom products;
Propose and design the best suitable ML and NLP models or algorithms based on the product requirements
Build ML pipelines such as model training, evaluation, and monitoring system and deploy in production utilizing AWS cloud;
Collaborate with various teams including offshore teams, communicating requirements, providing technical leadership, code review, production integration and deployment, and result evaluation.
Requirements
Ph.D or M.S. in NLP, Machine Learning, Computer Science or a related technical field;
Industry experience in machine learning applications in production.
Experience in developing pipeline components and processes, such as inference and training pipeline, model evaluation, monitoring, A/B testing etc.
Fluent in English writing and speaking, strong communication skills to work with different teams and stakeholders;
